<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Augsburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet gemäß altem Herkommen keinen Zoll von Waren Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute zu nehmen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_101" id="49r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_101_r3l26"><expan>Augſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_101_r3l27"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ etlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute fürbraht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l29">vnd cʒu vviſſen getan / vvie daʒ Jr von <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> habe vnd kaufmanſchaft </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_101_r3l28">wollen </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l31">beẏ ew cʒol cʒenemen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_101_r3l30">vnd <expan>ʒehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> maint 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd den <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> davon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l32">anders <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> das </del> von alter herkumen ſeẏ <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / Daʒ Jr durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l34"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute 
<add><ab facs="#facs_101_r3l33">
<del rend="strikethrough">an </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> mit <expan>ır<ex>er</ex></expan> habe vnd kauff </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l36">
<del rend="strikethrough">manſchaft </del> mit <expan>ſölche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vngevvönliche<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒölle vnbeſwert / ſunder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l37">ſie damit <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſen wöllet / als ſie von alter <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l38">Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / vnd lat vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_101_r3l39">vvıder wiſſen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Barth<ex>olomei</ex></expan> Anno octauo </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_101" id="49r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Augsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kauffleute fürbraht und czu wissen getan,
                        wie daz ir von <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>wollen</add> bey ew czol czenemen <add>und
                                <expan>zehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> maint, anders
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> von alter herkumen sey.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kauffleute mit
                            <expan>sölche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ungewönliche<ex>n</ex></expan> czölle unbeswert, sunder sie damit
                                <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen wöllet, als sie von alter
                                <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und lat uns des
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Barth<ex>olomei</ex></expan> anno octavo.</ab>
</div>
